Class FlowActivityEntity

  • java.lang.Object

      • org.apache.hadoop.yarn.api.records.timelineservice.FlowActivityEntity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<TimelineEntity>

    @InterfaceAudience.Public
 @InterfaceStability.Unstable
public class FlowActivityEntity
extends TimelineEntity
    Entity that represents a record for flow activity. It's essentially a container entity for flow runs with limited information.
